trend_summary: Imagery shows a maturing suburb: incremental residential infill, expansion of the northern campus, new commercial pads at the central interchange and wider arterial roads. Tree cover thins around new lots while green buffers stay along streams. Overall pattern remains a low-rise, car-oriented suburb that slowly densifies without tipping into full urban form.
notable_changes: Northern institutional campus gains several new buildings and larger parking decks.
Central cloverleaf/interchange upgraded and adjoining commercial parcels constructed.
